title: Gibson Dishwasher Filter
description: Gibson Dishwasher Filter ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 1 Review PartSelect Number PS11770489 Manufacturer Part Number 5304506525 This filter is for dishwashers. installationInstructions.title: Filters and drain trap extremely clogged, causing dishwasher not to drain and leak.
